display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-FashionCraze-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-FashionCraze_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.newspapers.com/clip/9232654//\">\"Believe it or NOT\"</a>. <i>The Record-Argus</i>. Greenville, Pennsylvania. May 13, 1933  &#8211; via <a href=\"/wiki/Newspapers.com\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Newspapers.com\">Newspapers.com</a> <span style=\"position:relative; top: -2px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Open_access\" title=\"open access publication \u2013 free to read\"><img alt=\"open access publication \u2013 free to read\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg/9px-Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg.png\" width=\"9\" height=\"14\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg/14px-Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg/18px-Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"640\" data-file-height=\"1000\" /></a></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Record-Argus&amp;rft.atitle=Believe+it+or+NOT&amp;rft.date=1933-05-13&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newspapers.com%2Fclip%2F9232654%2F%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALightning+rod+fashion\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-FOOTNOTEFiguier1867569-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEFiguier1867569_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"#CITEREFFiguier1867\">Figuier 1867</a>, p.&#160;569.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-FOOTNOTESoci\u00e9t\u00e9_fran\u00e7aise_des_\u